descriptionHtml:
Hi all, this is a simple save with a 2 meters Orc, i call him Totuk ( last shadow in Na\'vi ) i made him for the poeple who want a really big, strong a bloody 2h warrior.

Features:

The save is located at the cave after leave Helgen.
You have a leader armor and 2h sword, 2h hammer and 2h axe.
No money or quest finished.

please enjoy it and comment if you like it.

PD: drop the file on your Documents/mygames/skyrim/saves folder.
author: Gotika
